{"tid":273144,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"點解好似冇乜人講iPhone Wifi 有假死問題？","createTime":"2017-06-06T10:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T10:53:05.000Z","uid":10332,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"503ee2c8847a52a3fcb7abcb3bb37f02fdf2c674","tid":273144,"uid":10332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"Wifi 顯示收爆但冇連線能力<br />\n一係熄Wifi再開，一係等一陣，個Wifi icon 閃一下先再上得返<br />\n幾個朋友都有呢個現象，6s / 7 都有<br />\nGoogle 過都有人有呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n等過幾個firmware 都冇解決到<br />\n已經上過reset network setting<br />\n更試過reset all 重新裝過晒啲野<br />\n<br />\n呢個真係小眾問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13939c73fc60e952922fd5f4511ef0ccc0ba0791","tid":273144,"uid":30368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:42:48.000Z","msg":"上左10之後就有啦<br />\n屌到放棄左了"},{"pid":"5f4158e2124fa0c007a47197d9b835184136b51c","tid":273144,"uid":9758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:47:27.000Z","msg":"我仲以為我屋企router問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11407a9c510f1fc09740d420a4cb8ab21cf51871","tid":273144,"uid":5728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:48:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我仲以為我屋企router問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係router問題喎 重問部機又得返"},{"pid":"d9bd890acb802df475175205daa063a4b799c4e0","tid":273144,"uid":5728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我仲以為我屋企router問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係router問題喎 重開部機又得返</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3ef209be5db2061988c2f74fed3db971db6c316a","tid":273144,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"多數人成功而解決到的方法係換 router <br />\n<br />\n或者最後試下換 channel"},{"pid":"ea6b94f758849ec1338de4deeb29f1cd73fe8c69","tid"